3. **Hardware Product Development Stages**
   - EnCata. (2023). "Overview of Hardware Product Development Stages: POC – EVT – DVT – PVT"
   - [EnCata Blog](https://www.encata.net/blog/)

4. **Phase Gate Approach to Hardware Products**
   - Wevolver. (2021). "The Complete Guide to The Phase Gate Approach to Developing a Hardware Product"
   - [Wevolver Article](https://www.wevolver.com/article/phase-gate-approach-hardware-product)

